# Microsoft Graph API Configuration
# Get these values from Azure Portal > App Registrations > Your App

# Your Azure App Registration client ID
CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-here

# Your Azure App Registration client secret
CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-here

# Your Azure tenant ID
TENANT_ID=your-tenant-id-here

# Server Configuration (Optional)
PORT=8000
HOST=0.0.0.0

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual Azure credentials
# 3. To get these values:
#    - Go to https://portal.azure.com
#    - Navigate to App Registrations > Create or select your app
#    - CLIENT_ID: Copy from "Application (client) ID" on Overview page
#    - TENANT_ID: Copy from "Directory (tenant) ID" on Overview page
#    - CLIENT_SECRET: Go to "Certificates & secrets" > "New client secret" > Copy the Value
# 4. Ensure your app has these API permissions with admin consent:
#    - Files.ReadWrite.All
#    - Sites.ReadWrite.All
#    - User.Read.All
